ility to take direction and work cooperatively with others Working knowledge of Microsoft Excel, Word, Outlook Motivation to identify inefficiencies and creatively suggest ways to solve them Outstanding work ethic, integrity, and commitment Successful prior experience as an Administrative Assistant ", 
